metadata.name: Artist Mr.Milly
metadata.description:
Hello, this is Mr.Milly the shy face hiding behind this art and he is a new artist (Abstract Art) on web3. 
Maybe you won't understand what he is drawing but with your imagination you can see many things. He is new, but we all deserve a chance on art and making frens is free right? Let's connect and join in his journey, many more will be free for dark art lovers.

Byee, for now. =)
